attributes.title: Super Mario Maker
attributes.caption: ​Our story begins with Jeremy and Jack. Against low gamerscores, they were on the attack.  But once in a blue moon, they'd sit back and relax, And talk about life, old games, and some facts!
attributes.description: Our story begins with Jeremy and Jack.  Against low gamerscores, they were on the attack.  But once in a blue moon, they'd sit back and relax,  And talk about life, old games, and some facts!  And this was no different, no different at all.  At Franco's request, they answered the call.  There were facts about Mario, just ready to go.  If only Nintendo didn't stop and say no.  And now it's time to enjoy Mario Maker,  ...Uh...Kobe Bryant was an LA Laker?  Fuck this shit, man...rhyming is hard!  I mean, you need to be some kind of bard!  Oh hey, I did it! Just there, did you see?  I'm sorry this was long, don't fire me.  ~Thanks for everything, Joel Rubin!~
